<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, July 20 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 4,477.96 points on Monday, down 36.83
points, or 0.81 percent, from that on Friday.
</P>
<P>
The trade was heavy with the turnover of over 93 trillion
Turkish Liras (about 345 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
There were 97 gainers and 116 losers.
</P>
<P>
The financial index closed at 5,508.79, down 72.23 points, or
1.29 percent and industrial index closed at 3,756.53, down 23.72
points, or 0.62 percent, from Friday's finishes.
</P>
<P>
However, the service index gained 85.48 points, or 1.62
percent, to close at 5,399.89 points from Friday's
closing. 
</P>
</TEXT>
