<TEXT>
<P>
BAGHDAD, July 20 (Xinhua) -- Iraq on Monday slammed a comment
broadcast by the Voice of America which said the Democratic
People's Republic of Korea had sold missiles to Iraq and the
United Nations had found VX gas on Iraqi missile warheads.
</P>
<P>
The Iraqi News Agency quoted the political editor at
Al-Jumhoriya (Republic) Radio Station as saying on Monday that
the claims on VX gas was made by a biased party -- U.S. army
