Charles Josselin made the declaration after a meeting with the
Nigerian head of state, General Abdulsalam Abukabar, in the
Nigerian capital Abuja.
</P>
<P>
AFP quoted Josselin as saying that he had delivered "a message
of understanding" from the French government to Abukabar.
</P>
