<P>
LAGOS, July 20 (Xinhua) -- Nigerian Head of State General
Abdulsalam Abubakar has pardoned and ordered the immediate
release of 10 convicts of the 1995 coup plot, the state TV NTA
reported Monday.
</P>
<P>
The release, signed by David Attah, the Chief Press Secretary
to the head of state, was announced in a statement in federal
capital Abuja, the report said.
</P>
