<HEADLINE> France Again Delays National Coach Appointment </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, July 21 (Xinhua) -- The French Football Federation (FFF) said
Tuesday it has again delayed the appointment of a successor to Aime Jacquet,
who resigned as French coach after winning the World Cup.
</P>
<P>
FFF had planned to name a new coach last week and then on Friday said the
appointment would come by the middle of this week.
</P>
