<TEXT>
<P>
MAPUTO, July 21 (Xinhua) -- Organizers of the Maputo
International Fair announced that eight countries have been
confirmed to attend the fair, including France, Holland and China
which will be present at the fair after years of interval.
</P>
<P>
The organizers made the announcement here Monday in a
communique. Portugal, Norway, Britain, South Africa, Botswana
will also participate in the fair, the Noticias newspaper Tuesday
quoted the communique as saying.
</P>
<P>
