<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, July 21 (Xinhua) -- A man injured in a horror
bus crash in Libode, Eastern Cape, died Tuesday morning, bringing
to 15 the number of deaths in the accident, South African Press
Association (SAPA) reported.
</P>
<P>
The man died while being transferred to a ward in St. Barnabas
Hospital, said the South African news agency.
</P>
<P>
