no plans to deploy troops in Macedonia, let alone adopt any form
of military intervention" in clashes in Kosovo.
</P>
<P>
"Now we think the best way is to keep the U.N. Preventive
Deployment Forces (UNPREDF) in Macedonia longer," Solana told the
Macedonian daily New Macedonia, which carried the report on
Monday. (Macedonia-NATO-Military Deployment)
</P>
