<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading South African </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, July 21 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news
items in leading South African newspapers Tuesday:
</P>
<P>
The Citizen:
</P>
<P>
-- No decision on the purchase of armament for the South
African National Defense Force would be made until the
counter-trade proposals accompanying tenders had been evaluated,
South African Defense Minister Joe Modise said Monday.
</P>
