telecommunications center or an electricity transformer. Over 25
such installations had been attacked in the past one month.
</P>
<P>
With the South Asian Association for Regional Cooperation
summit scheduled to commence in Colombo on July 29 security in and
around Colombo has been stepped up.
</P>
<P>
However, the police do not believe that the latest find of
explosives was to be directed at the SAARC leaders. 
