<HEADLINE> Beijing-Hebei Cooperation Called for </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHIJIAZHUANG July 21 (Xinhua) -- Increased cooperation between
Beijing and Hebei Province, which surrounds the city, will play an
important role in economic development of the Bohai Sea rim,
according to Beijing Mayor Jia Qinglin.
</P>
