<P>
The two have had a lot of cooperation in industry, agriculture,
commerce, and trade, he said, and added that that the capital city
will do its best to promote cooperation that focuses on open and
competitive markets, improved industrial structure, technological
cooperation, personnel exchanges, foreign trade, tourism and
developing urban construction and agricultural resources. 
</P>
